@startuml SD-07
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-07: Login Admin & Akses Dashboard

actor "Admin\n(Browser)" as Admin #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(AuthController)" as Auth #2E8B57
participant "Middleware\n(auth+admin)" as MW #E74C3C
participant "AdminController" as Dashboard #F39C12
database "MySQL\n(Database)" as DB #3498DB
participant "ChatbotService" as Service #50C878

== 1. Admin Buka Halaman Login ==
Admin -> Auth : GET /login
activate Auth
Auth --> Admin : Tampilkan form login\n(email + password)
deactivate Auth

== 2. Admin Submit Login ==
Admin -> Auth : POST /login\n{email: "admin@rsj.com",\npassword: "password123"}
activate Auth

note right of Auth
  Validasi:
  - email: wajib, format email
  - password: wajib
end note

Auth -> DB : SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE email = "admin@rsj.com"
activate DB
DB --> Auth : user ditemukan\n{id:1, role:"super_admin",\npassword: "$2y$10$..."}
deactivate DB

Auth -> Auth : Auth::attempt(credentials)
note right of Auth
  Bandingkan hash password
  → Cocok! Login berhasil
end note

Auth -> Auth : session()->regenerate()
Auth --> Admin : Redirect → /admin\n(Set-Cookie: session)
deactivate Auth

== 3. Akses Dashboard Admin ==
Admin -> Dashboard : GET /admin\n(Cookie: session)
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> MW : Cek middleware auth + admin
activate MW
MW -> MW : Auth::check() → true\nUser::role → "super_admin" ✓
MW --> Dashboard : Lewat (authorized)
deactivate MW

== 4. Kumpulkan Data Dashboard ==
Dashboard -> DB : COUNT(*) FROM chatbot_feedback
activate DB
DB --> Dashboard : totalFeedback = 156
deactivate DB

Dashboard -> DB : COUNT(*) FROM data_ruangans
activate DB
DB --> Dashboard : totalRooms = 85
deactivate DB

Dashboard -> DB : SELECT DATE, SUM(is_correct),...\nGROUP BY date
activate DB
DB --> Dashboard : akurasi per hari (chart data)
deactivate DB

Dashboard -> DB : SELECT feedback + ruangan\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 20
activate DB
DB --> Dashboard : recentFeedbacks (paginated)
deactivate DB

Dashboard -> Service : Cache::get('last_sync_time')
activate Service
Service --> Dashboard : "19/06/2026 10:30:00"
deactivate Service

== 5. Tampilkan Dashboard ==
Dashboard --> Admin : Render view admin.dashboard\n(stats, chart, feedback log)
deactivate Dashboard

note over Admin
  Dashboard menampilkan:
  - Total chat: 2.025
  - Total feedback: 156
  - Akurasi model AI: 96%
  - Grafik akurasi harian
  - Log feedback terbaru
  - Tombol sinkronisasi model
end note

@enduml
